description: Sweet! The Mobile Cupcakery is a food truck based in Columbus, OH bringing gourmet cupcakes to a street corner near you!We also deliver cupcakes (with or without the cupcake truck or bus) to locations and events in the greater Cleveland and greater Columbus areas. For an awesome addition to your event, the cupcake truck and bus are available to provide scrumptious cupcakes to weddings, birthdays, graduations, block parties, business meetings and even promotional and corporate events. There are endless possibilities to make Sweet! The Mobile Cupcakery part of your next event.
name: Sweet! The Mobile Cupcakery
